  "system": {
    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Granite Wards hold ground. They plant themselves where the summoner indicates and do not move unless ordered to. Earth Bond makes attrition against them on natural surfaces a slow process. They function best as mobile obstacles — position one in a doorway, narrow pass, or between the summoner and the enemy and it will remain there performing exactly that function until something removes it.</p>"
