    "tactics": "",
    "attacksNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Slam [Combat]:</strong> Melee attack (Agi 2 + Melee Combat 4), Reach: 5 ft\n<ul>\n<li><em>Margin 1:</em> 6 damage (standard natural weapon)</li>\n<li><em>Margin 2:</em> 11 damage (6 + 5 Str); target knocked Prone; no save</li>\n<li><em>Margin 3:</em> 11 damage + Prone; target Restrained by earth and stone until they succeed on a Might check (Hard task, 2 successes) as a [Combat] action</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>",
    "specialAbilitiesNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Immovable:</strong> Cannot be knocked Prone by non-magical forced movement. Shoves automatically fail unless the attacker wins an opposed Strength + Athletics check (Hard task, 2 successes).</li>\n<li><strong>Earth Bond:</strong> While standing on natural earth or stone, regains 4 HP at the start of its turn. Suppressed if it took magical damage this round.</li>\n</ul>",
    "reactionsNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Stone Skin [Reaction]:</strong> Once per round when hit by a physical attack, reduce incoming damage by 4.</li>\n</ul>",
